Description

Riyadh Golf City, born from the success of its Predecessor, Riyadh Tech City, this new masterpiece of crafts and expertise stands tall as an embodiment of modernity intertwined with the pleasure and soothing ease that comes with the serenity that the calm waves of Asadam ocean has to offer.
Riyadh Tech City sold Out and its success has inspired Us to dream bigger and better. A Community where relaxation and fun are seen as bringing contemporary status to life. A home must be an abode for relaxation and productivity.
Welcome to Riyadh Golf City, where elegance is infused in a never seen touch of ingenuity for the privileged few who understands luxury and urban landscape.

The Location
